# Awesome Forum Website

Welcome to Awesome Forum, a modern and user-friendly forum website built with Laravel! This project is dockerized for easy deployment and development. Whether you're a developer looking to contribute or a user exploring the features, we're glad to have you on board!

## Features

- User Authentication: Register, login, and manage your profile.
- Forum Categories: Organize discussions into different categories.
- Thread Creation: Start new discussions within categories.
- Thread Replies: Engage in conversations by replying to threads.
- Markdown Support: Format your posts using Markdown syntax.
- Dockerized: Simplified deployment and development with Docker.

## Installation

To get started with this project locally, follow these steps:

1. Clone this repository: `git clone https://github.com/your-username/awesome-forum.git`
2. Navigate to the project directory: `cd awesome-forum`
3. Build and run Docker containers: `docker-compose up -d`
4. Access the website at `http://localhost:8000`

For detailed instructions on deploying and configuring the project, refer to the [documentation](docs/).

